		"description": "DOCUMENTATION: A flaw was found in Grafana. This flaw allows a malicious user with the authorization to log into a Grafana instance via a configured OAuth IdP to take over an existing Grafana account under certain conditions. \n            \n            MITIGATION: As a workaround, it is possible to disable any OAuth login or ensure that all users authorized to log in via OAuth have a corresponding user account in Grafana linked to their email address.",
